Hi, I am using Terraform to deploy Azure resources (Function App, Key Vault, Storage, Insights).
Since I only have Contributor permission, Terraform cannot auto-register Resource Providers.
Can you please run the following commands once on the subscription?

az provider register --namespace Microsoft.Web
az provider register --namespace Microsoft.Storage
az provider register --namespace Microsoft.KeyVault
az provider register --namespace Microsoft.Insights
az provider register --namespace Microsoft.EventHub


